cmput301w15t07.TravelTracker.model

Interface DataSource

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeneratedDataSource, InMemoryDataSource

    public interface DataSource
    Interface for serving model Documents from any persistent storage class. Implementations should inherit from Observable so views may observe.
    Author:
    kdbanman
